MUSICIAN Lvovo Derango took to Twitter to thank Zakes Bantwini to thank him for the role he played in his development as an artist. In an emotional post, he said how much he loved Zakes and how thanked him for “seeing something in me”. He wrote: Thank u for believing in me and guiding me to be a person I am today u saw something that no one saw even myself u told me how I should protect this brand called Lvovo I hope u proud and I’m still going strong thank u so much for everything we I LOVE U @ZakesBantwiniSA 